doc.excludeDomains: Ngeta emagama esizinda kutsi angafakwa Ligama lesizinda linye kuphela lelingangetwa ngesikhatsi sinye.

example.domain: Ungangeta ligama lesizinda, njenge {{url}}, kute ungafaki lonkhe ligama lesizinda.
example.url: Ungakhipha tikhonjiso letitsite ngekwengeta sikhonjiso, njenge {{url}}.
example.glob: Ungangeta iphethini {{glob}}, njenge <khodi>{{kufana lokuncane}}</khodi>, yekuhambisana lokungacacile.

doc.script: Ungaphindze usebentise imibhalo ye-js kute ufinyelele kulawula lokuyinkimbinkimbi kakhulu.
doc.checkedUseScript: Noma ngabe unika script sakho emandla, caphela kutsi kufanele uhlole womabili lamabhokisi ngesikhatsi sinye kute unikete script emandla.

example1.commentTitle: Kwanyalo kuwebhusayithi ye {{youtube}}, kufanele uvule likhasi le {{bukela}} noma {{emafishane}} kuthebhu lensha.

example1.minimatch: : indlela yekufanisa {{glob}}, usebentisa umtapolwati {{kufanisa lokuncane}}, indlela yekusebentisa Sicela Bona, noma ungasesha indlela yekusebentisa {{glob}}.
example1.wholeCode: Inshokutsi yayo yonkhe ikhodi kutsi njengamanje ekhasini leligama lesizinda le-YouTube {{www}}, uma ngabe sixhumanisi lesichafatwe ligama lesizinda lelifanako futsi indlela icala nga {{watch}} noma {{shorts}}, bese kuba nethebhu lensha . likhasi lelisesandleni sekudla litawuvulwa.
